{"tid":2489594,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"筆裡灌水「活跳跳寄生蟲」狂扭！日本超噁觀光紀念品　看久有點夢幻啊","createTime":"2021-04-15T04:51:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T04:51:49.000Z","uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d2c12fd1da44483a883a5320caa93912a46763bb","tid":2489594,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T04:51:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EyHUflvUYAETq29?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEyHUflvUYAETq29%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dsmall&h=0c416cd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/i/status/1378618541247623170\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fi%2Fstatus%2F1378618541247623170&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sJNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=9f72ef58\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fi%2Fstatus%2F1378618541247623170&h=c1aa701e\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/i/status/1378618541247623170</a><br />\n<br />\n這是日本高知縣一處漁業盛地，當地的店家推出的特別商品，在筆蓋那邊放進水跟幾隻海<br />\n獸胃線蟲，當作特產來賣。<br />\n <br />\n修但幾勒！這個海獸胃線蟲名字裡有蟲，那牠是蟲嗎？<br />\n <br />\n對！而且牠是一種本體白色的寄生蟲！但是不會這麼大隻寄生在人類體內發育長大啦～牠<br />\n們都通常會寄生在海裡的魚類身上，只是你各位吃生魚肉的時候有機率會吃到牠們的幼蟲<br />\n，會讓吃下肚的人類肚子痛或產生過敏反應！<br />\n <br />\n大概放進去原子筆後，它會在裡面活跳跳個4到5天，然後就慢慢地不動了，好像在上生物<br />\n課呢......<br />\n <br />\n日本網友紛紛表示真的很稀奇，但是買了這樣的商品會讓人想去保健室報到！<br />\n <br />\n我看了都莫名覺得肚子開始痛了起來，你各位喜歡就買，我就不+1了啊～～<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/dalemon/post/53996\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fdalemon%2Fpost%2F53996&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sJNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=4b674e09\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/dalemon/post/53996</a>"},{"pid":"46b3cf4b4afdf099af292e4fdec81b60675fe74d","tid":2489594,"uid":55386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T04:51:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}